DOC.criteria: Have body mass index ( BMI ) ≥18 ≤30 kg/m2 weight ≥50 kg ≤100 kg . Regular daily bowel movement ( ie , production least 1 stool per day ) . Nonsmoker exsmoker use tobacco nicotine product ≥6 month prior Visit 1 Healthy Male volunteer age 50 Healthy volunteer expose radiation level background ( eg , Xray examination ) > 5 mSv last year , > 10 mSv last 5 year , cumulative total > 1 mSv per year life Participation prior radiolabelled study within last 5 year History alcohol abuse excessive intake alcohol judge investigator .
